trong>Stairway Mortgage handles Florida attorney borrowers across BigLaw partnership + non-equity partner + solo practice + plaintiff contingency + government attorney structures with deep understanding of K-1 capital account mechanics, contingency fee continuity narrative, Florida tort reform context, and multi-source synthesis.</strong> Or skip ahead: <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/loan-programs/jumbo-loan/" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px;">Jumbo loan details</a>, <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/loan-programs/" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px;">every loan program</a>, <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/loan-calculator/" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px;">mortgage calculators</a>, or <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/current-rates/" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px;">today&apos;s rates</a>.</p>
