        </div>
        <div class="key-fact-card">
          <div class="key-fact-num">Multi-source synthesis</div>
          <p class="key-fact-body">Attorney multi-source income varies dramatically by practice structure. BigLaw: W-2 + K-1 + originator. Solo: Schedule C + PLLC. Contingency: episodic large recoveries. Government: stable W-2. Stairway synthesizes each component under appropriate framework producing single DTI-ready qualifying figure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="key-fact-card">
          <div class="key-fact-num">Capital account mechanics</div>
