  <!-- ============ H2 #2: ATTORNEY PRACTICE ROLES ============ -->
  <section class="professions-section section-tinted" id="attorney-roles">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="eyebrow">02 &middot; Florida attorney practice roles</div>
        <h2>The five attorney practice roles spanning the Florida attorney income spectrum.</h2>
        <p>Florida attorneys practice under <a href="https://www.flsenate.gov/Laws/Statutes/2024/Chapter454" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Florida Statutes Chapter 454</a> Bar admission across five primary practice structures with distinct income mechanics + qualifying considerations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="professions-grid">

        <div class="profession-card">
