          <ul class="profession-points">
            <li>K-1 distribution $750K-$5M+ tier</li>
            <li>Capital contribution $200K-$1M+</li>
            <li>Partnership agreement governance</li>
            <li>AmLaw 100/200 firm tier</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="profession-link" style="opacity: 0.65;">See BigLaw partner qualifying below</span>
        </div>

